&gt;&gt; &quot; I don&#39;t know where we can find a repair chamber, but this should help 
&gt;&gt; you find just a little bit more energy. It&#39;s my last reserve, but you 
&gt;&gt; need this more than I do. Here, drink, it&#39;s energon, and it will help you 
&gt;&gt; keep some energy in your body.&quot;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; At the same time, Tucson was keeping an ear out for the metallic spiders 
&gt;&gt; and insects. His pace steady, as he continues to walk forward, keeping 
&gt;&gt; his headlights a blaze to light his way.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &quot;We&#39;ll get through this Vestige, I promise you.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; Vestige&#39;s systems flicker and sputter as Tuscon feeds him the energon
&gt; and then with a small burst of energy his optics brighten. &quot;Thank you
&gt; Tuscon.&quot; he said, his voice horse and raspy but clearer than before.
&gt; It is obvious that although Vestige is doing a little better he is
&gt; still in need of repairs. For some reason his self repair circuits do
&gt; not seem to be healing as effeciently as they should.
&gt;
&gt; He nods as Tuscon promised to get them through, &quot;I . . . I don&#39;t know
&gt; why, but I feel as if I can trust you.&quot; he says, his voice weak but
&gt; still clear. With a shaky arm he points further down the path that
&gt; Tuscon is taking them, &quot;There is where I must go, down there. The
&gt; chamber where I need to be sits there.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; The direction that Vestige points is simply a long hallways, that
&gt; after maybe 30 yards or so bends around a corner and apparently
&gt; continues on. There are doors on either side of the hall at different
&gt; points, and lights on the cieling illuminate the hall ahead. So far
&gt; there is no evidence of insects, and whatever scraping noise that was
&gt; heard before seems to be much further away.
&gt;
&gt; Vestige climbes unsteadily to his feet, and much like an old man
&gt; attempts to hobble slowly down the hall, seemingly focused on the task
&gt; ahead. &quot;Come.&quot; he says, his voice weak, but now filled with a grim
&gt; determination.
